snippet.textDisplay: 2:39 Kudos to Coke studio Bharat for including the original form of song+storytelling which has been the standard in Gujarati folk. Khalasi (sailors) from Khambhat/Kathiyawar region used to sing a lot of these songs in their long voyages. This song encapsulates their zeal and valour. And it's only befitting that the roaring voice from Gujarat Aditya Gadhvi delivers this banger❤️🔥
